   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Healing children and youth in Sri Lanka</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will fund the Shanthi Maargam &quot;Art of Living&quot; youth center which provides free professional counseling, mindfulness meditation, art and music therapy to strengthen the emotional well-being of children and youth in low-income multi ethno-religious communities in Colombo. Children and Youth develop skills to manage emotions, find a deeper level of peace, and in the long-term learn to break the cycle of violence in their families and communities.</narrative>
  </description>
